    All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<E>, java.util.Collection<E>, java.util.List<E>, EList<E>, InternalEList<E>

    @ParametersAreNonnullByDefault
public class ContentsList<E extends EObject>
extends AbstractSequentialInternalEList<E>
    A read-only sequential List that delegates its operations to the associated Store.

    Instances of this class are created by EObject.eContents() and allows to access the content of a PersistentEObject by lazily loading the elements.
